data.title: Under The Sea Birthday Party Gable Box Label
data.text:
This listing is for an editable digital printable gable box label . Nothing personalized or physical will be shipped.

Please read all the description before purchasing.

★••★ CLICK HERE TO TRY THE DEMO BEFORE BUYING ★••★

★••★ HOW DOES THIS WORK? ★••★

1. Purchase the item.

2. You will receive an email from CORJL.COM within a few minutes with a direct link to access your template. If you don't receive it, please contact us.

3. Edit the sign with your info.

*You can use your phone or a computer. With your phone you can change the text, for major edits you'll need to use a computer.

*While almost all of the texts are editable, in some cases there are exceptions. Please check the demo to see what parts are editable before purchasing.

4. Save your changes, and choose your preferred file format: JPG or PDF.

5. Print your files at home or in a print shop.

★••★ INCLUDED WITH YOUR PURCHASE ★••★

- 5x3 inches editable label.

✔ No software needed.

✔ Edit instantly with your phone or computer (Try the demo to see what is editable on this template).

✔ Add text as needed.

✔ Change font size, style and color.

✔ Add Images.

✔ Save as JPG or PDF to print at an online printshop or copy center.

★••★ IMPORTANT ★••★

*This is a digital file and no physical items will be mailed to you.

*Colors may vary between online viewing and your actual printed product. All computer monitors display color differently as well as all printers print differently. So please take this into consideration when viewing your design.

*Your template will be available in your Corjl account for 90 days.

*Refunds are not accepted, but please contact us if you have any problem with your order.

★••★ PERSONAL USE ★••★
